'''紀洛姆·尼克婁'''（{{lang-fr|Guillaume Nicloux}})是[[法國|法國]]小說家、導演與演員，他寫了數本犯罪小說，並同時執導電影與電視劇。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne-26856/biographie/|title=Guillaume Nicloux : Sa biographie|language=fr|work=[[AlloCiné|AlloCiné]]|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-date=2018-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180501115111/http://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne-26856/biographie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他所執導的《綁架大作家》在[[翠貝卡電影節|2014年翠貝卡電影節]]獲得最佳劇本獎。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tribecafilm.com/filmguide/archive/53208ba4c07f5df7d2000a8f-best-screenplay-narrative|title=Best Screenplay Narrative Winner: The Kidnapping of Michel Houellebecq|work=tribecafilm.com|publisher=[[Tribeca_Film_Festival|Tribeca Film Festival]]|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074929/https://tribecafilm.com/filmguide/archive/53208ba4c07f5df7d2000a8f-best-screenplay-narrative|dead-url=no}}</ref>

